242
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:04,030
as Crown Prince’s study partner,

243
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,320
so that you can become friends

244
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,030
to protect you,

245
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:12,030
