261
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:58,080
You were just greedy!

262
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,960
Yan Hui promised to help your

263
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,720
granddaughter be the Crown Princess.

264
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:17,750
